Exceptional Home - In Prime Position
This meticulously maintained presented four bedroom home offers a first class living environment.
Sited on a prime elevated block in a highly sought after location. This Rio Vista Court property is only a short stroll to the banks of the Murray River and walking tracks.

Description:
Well presented family home
This well presented family home offers two living areas and three bedrooms. It is separated into two zones, with the master bedroom enjoying the formal lounge room with its wood heater to sit by on those cold winter nights. And the second living area located at the back of the home with the two bedrooms making it ideal for a place for the kids to zone out. The kitchen divides the two spaces and overlooks the outdoor entertaining area. It comprises electric cooktop, wall oven tower, microwave space and dishwasher. The master bedroom has ensuite and walk in robe and is spacious in size. The family bathroom has shower over bath, vanity and separate toilet. The climate is controlled throughout with gas ducted heating and evaporative cooling. Externally there is a double carport, 6m x 3.4m colorbond shed and rear yard access through the double gates into a generous sized rear yard.

Description:
Lot 58 Dudley Park Lane
This stunning new four bedroom home is ready to move into. Boasting contemporary features and a neutral colour pallet throughout.
The kitchen is fitted with a double stainless steel sink, gas cook top, oven, butlers pantry and has ample cupboard and bench space.
With an open kitchen living and dining area this home will suit any family. Timber flooring throughout with carpet in the bedrooms; Main with ensuite.
Large undercover outdoor area with a low maintenance rear yard. Rear roller door access from the double garage. This home is located near sporting facilities, schools, and is surrounded by new homes.

Description:
River End Location - Immaculate Home!
This top quality four bedroom home is superbly presented and in absolutely immaculate condition, the ideal family home!
Features include spacious open plan kitchen/living/meals area with sliding doors opening to the undercover outdoor area. Four bedrooms, main with built in robes & ensuite with separate toilet. New carpet and repainted throughout.
Ducted heating and cooling, ducted vacuum system and double lock up garage with rear roller door for drive through access to rear yard. Outside features a generous undercover entertainment area, 3m x 4m garden shed and rainwater tank.
Perfectly manicured garden surrounds, not a thing out of place! Excellent Court location only a very short walk to the Murray River. A must to inspect!

Description:
Retire In Style
Set in Cobram's Green Palms Retirement Village is this beautiful and spacious three bedroom, two bathroom home.
Features large living areas with high ceilings. Great sized, stylish kitchen with a breakfast bar, pantry and stainless steel appliances. Three bedrooms with built in robes, the main with ensuite. Reverse cycle split system heating and cooling, and single lockup garage with electric roller door.
Excellent undercover outdoor entertaining area, front verandah/pati with blinds, and a covered deck in the rear yard. There's also 12 panel solar system installed to assist in reducing electricity costs.
A modern, appealing and low maintenance home perfect for those wanting to retire in style.
